{"tid":692500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實毒撚好多時都係屋企造成","createTime":"2018-06-06T17:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T10:52:35.000Z","uid":58316,"like":75,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b2e8761c33df81d812ece525039b6d64cfeb1f","tid":692500,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T17:09:46.000Z","msg":"唔俾呢樣唔俾個樣<br />\n要咪書<br />\n唔俾出夜街<br />\n唔俾拍拖<br />\n話要等讀完書先<br />\n落街食飯話俾你揀<br />\n想食xx飯會叫你揀過第樣<br />\n揀到啱佢心水為止<br />\n細個唔做數<br />\n俾老母扑爛部世嘉<br />\n小學有條友<br />\n人生=補習+練琴+奧數<br />\n每日淨係准睇半粒鐘新聞<br />\n有叮噹睇已經係好奢侈<br />\n郁d打鬧，樓上樓下聽到哂<br />\n衫褲鞋襪全部屋企買<br />\n<br />\n人大左<br />\n睇過好多單殺人狂新聞<br />\n都係由細到大俾老豆老母恰<br />\n秋葉原<br />\n雪櫃藏屍<br />\n台北捷運<br />\n個犯都係毒撚黎<br />\n係呢d高壓家庭出世仲慘過窮"},{"pid":"d2ba2399b93eca18194311705967be5761443d83","tid":692500,"uid":183691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T17:12:09.000Z","msg":"中肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ff014e72882116f0e351be51bbf96e2674bb26","tid":692500,"uid":146476,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"依家都係 <br />\n出街食飯 問你想食乜嘢. <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 今晚唔煮飯 出去食. 你揀想食咩啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 譚仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 食咩麵呀 晚餐食乜鬼麵 食飯唔好咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :......  ( X你咪又係茶記)<br />\n<br />\n仲要次次都係咁. 從來未試過同佢一齊食譚仔.   然後都係去茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb383956c81d5793b6b45cf8f4c5a9dce833391","tid":692500,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T17:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"h